          "caption": "Today's pull: Healing ✨. Wounds become light.\nMended with care, your cracks become golden seams.\nWhat old wound is quietly becoming your strength?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #motivation #selfdevelopment #healing #kintsugi"
