          "cardNumber": 46,
          "story": "The bamboo bends deep in the fierce wind and does not snap, while stiffer things break. Strength is not always about holding rigid; often it is the willingness to flex with what comes. Bend where you must today, and you will still be standing when the wind dies down.",
          "caption": "Today's pull: Adaptability 🎋. Bend, don't break.\nThe rigid snap in the storm; the flexible survive it.\nWhere could a little flexibility serve you better than force?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #motivation #selfdevelopment #adaptability #flexibility"
