          "caption": "Today's pull: Ambition 🌟. Aim for the stars.\nReaching high stretches you, even if you don't touch every star.\nWhat goal feels almost too big to say out loud?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #motivation #selfdevelopment #ambition #aimhigh"
