          "description": "Kindness",
          "cardNumber": 50,
          "story": "One small candle leans to light another, and soon a whole chain of flames spreads into the dark. Kindness costs you nothing yet changes everything, passing quietly from one person to the next. The smallest warm gesture you offer today may travel far beyond your sight.",
