          "caption": "Today's pull: Deer 🦌. Gentleness is strength.\n\nSoftness isn't a weakness to fix. It's power that stopped needing to prove itself.\nWhere could you be gentle today instead of guarded?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #poweranimals #spiritanimal #deer #gentleness"
