          "caption": "Today's pull: Fox 🦊. Be smarter, not harder.\n\nPushing harder isn't always progress. Sometimes the clever path is shorter.\nWhere are you forcing what you could finesse?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #poweranimals #spiritanimal #fox #cleverness"
