          "caption": "Today's pull: Face Fear Directly 🦁. Meet what scares you.\n\nThe thing you keep glancing away from grows in the dark. Turn toward it. What would you see?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #courage #wisdom #facingfear #innerstrength"
