          "caption": "Today's pull: The Cost of Not Trying 🚪. Regret runs deep.\n\nWe fear failing, but rarely weigh the cost of the attempt we never made. Which door would haunt you?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #courage #wisdom #noregrets #takethechance"
