          "description": "Let It Be, Then Let It Go",
          "cardNumber": 49,
          "story": "First let the feeling simply be: no fixing, no fighting, just allowing it to exist in your open hand. Then, when it has been fully felt, let it drift away on its own breeze. Allowing and releasing are two halves of the same gentle motion.",
