          "description": "Steady the Inner Sea",
          "cardNumber": 50,
          "story": "When your inner waters churn, you cannot force them flat, but you can stop stirring and let them settle on their own. Slowly the chop smooths into a mirror, calm enough to reflect a single steady star. Quiet the sea within, and clarity rises to meet you.",
