          "description": "Appreciate the People Now",
          "cardNumber": 20,
          "story": "Two chairs at a small table, one still warm with someone dear. The people beside you will not always be in that chair, and the moment holds more weight than it lets on. Look up from your busyness and see them while they are here. Say it, mean it, and let them feel appreciated now.",
