          "caption": "Today's pull: Ego Is the Enemy 🪞. See clearly.\n\nThe version of you that needs to look big is the one that keeps you small.\nWho's really talking: you, or the shadow?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #humility #ego #selfawareness #mindset"
