          "caption": "Today's pull: The Beginner's Humility 🏺. Be willing to be bad.\n\nEvery master was once happy to make something lopsided.\nWhat have you avoided starting because you might look clumsy?\nPull your card → @dailycard (link in bio)\n\n#dailycard #humility #ego #beginnersmind #growth"
